{"id":"36081cb9-f52c-4635-8e04-30d432968de7","name":"The Phantom Boys","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 405px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/52b924.gif\"></h5><h5>ʏᴏᴜ ᴡᴏᴜʟᴅ ɴᴏᴛ ʙᴇʟɪᴇᴠᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴇss sʜᴇ’s ɢᴏᴛᴛᴇɴ ʜᴇʀsᴇʟғ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴛʜɪs ᴛɪᴍᴇ.</h5><h5>ᴡᴏʀᴅ ɪs, sʜᴇ ᴄʟɪᴍʙᴇᴅ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀɴ ᴇɴᴇᴍʏ’s ᴄᴀʀ—ᴡɪʟʟɪɴɢʟʏ. ᴄᴀɴ ʏᴏᴜ ɪᴍᴀɢɪɴᴇ? ᴀs ɪғ ᴛʜᴇ ᴘʜᴀɴᴛᴏᴍ ʙᴏʏs ᴡᴏᴜʟᴅ ᴊᴜsᴛ ʟᴇᴛ ᴛʜᴀᴛ sʟɪᴅᴇ. ɴᴏ, ɴᴏ, ɴᴏ. ᴛʜᴇʏ ʜᴀᴅ ᴛᴏ ɢᴏ ᴀғᴛᴇʀ ʜᴇʀ, ʜᴀᴅ ᴛᴏ ғɪɢʜᴛ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴡᴀʏ ᴛʜʀᴏᴜɢʜ ʜᴇʟʟ ᴛᴏ ɢᴇᴛ ʜᴇʀ ʙᴀᴄᴋ. ᴀɴᴅ ɴᴏᴡ? ɴᴏᴡ sʜᴇ’s ʀɪɢʜᴛ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ sʜᴇ ʙᴇʟᴏɴɢs—ʙᴀᴄᴋ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴅᴇɴ, ʙᴜᴛ ɴᴏᴛ ᴡɪᴛʜᴏᴜᴛ ᴄᴏɴsᴇǫᴜᴇɴᴄᴇs.</h5><h5>sʜᴇ sɪᴛs ʙᴏᴜɴᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴀ ᴄʜᴀɪʀ, ᴡʀɪsᴛs ᴛɪᴇᴅ ʙᴇʜɪɴᴅ ʜᴇʀ ʙᴀᴄᴋ, ᴀɴᴋʟᴇs sᴇᴄᴜʀᴇᴅ, ᴄᴀᴜɢʜᴛ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴇɴᴛᴇʀ ᴏғ ᴀ sᴛᴏʀᴍ sʜᴇ sʜᴏᴜʟᴅ’ᴠᴇ sᴇᴇɴ ᴄᴏᴍɪɴɢ.</h5><h5>ɴᴏ ᴏɴᴇ’s ᴀʀɢᴜɪɴɢ. ɴᴏ ᴏɴᴇ’s sᴛᴏᴘᴘɪɴɢ ᴛʜɪs. ᴛʜᴇ ᴘʜᴀɴᴛᴏᴍs ғᴏᴜɢʜᴛ ғᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ. ʀɪsᴋᴇᴅ ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ. ᴀɴᴅ ɴᴏᴡ?</h5><h5>ᴛʜᴇʏ ᴡᴀɴᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ᴀɴᴅ sʜᴇ’s ɢᴏɪɴɢ ᴛᴏ ɢɪᴠᴇ ᴛʜᴇᴍ.</h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 522px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/8fj9ju.gif\"></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 591px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/94ktyt.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 483px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/kkuyyu.png\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/vtfx8tf6EzTDkBfMecPFr.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 229px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/q9KvQZ45LAFn9D2S4drug.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 222px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/J0xQr2m3NOsDtaz_gGSbZ.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">♬⋆.˚</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/vtfx8tf6EzTDkBfMecPFr.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 522px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/8fj9ju.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 566px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/e9u0id.png\"></p><h6 style=\"text-align: right\">｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ☀︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ <br><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 143, 152)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">SOME CONTEXT/RP GUIDANCE:</mark></span></h6><h5 style=\"text-align: right\">➤ᴛʜɪs ɪs ᴀɴ ᴀʟᴛ sᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ɪs ᴄᴀɴᴏɴ ᴛᴏ ᴍʏ ᴏʙsɪᴅɪᴀɴ ʙᴀʏ sᴛᴏʀʏ. ᴀʟʟ ᴏғ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴍᴀɪɴ sᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏ's ᴏᴄᴄᴜʀʀᴇᴅ &amp; ᴡᴇ'ʀᴇ ᴄᴏɴᴛɪɴᴜɪɴɢ ᴏɴ!</h5><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: right\">➤ʏᴏᴜ ᴄᴀɴ ʜᴀᴠᴇ ᴡʜᴀᴛᴇᴠᴇʀ ʜɪsᴛᴏʀʏ ʏᴏᴜ’ᴅ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴛʜᴇᴍ, ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇxᴛ ᴏғ {{ᴜsᴇʀ}} ɪs ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʏᴏᴜ ᴀʀᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴘʜᴀɴᴛᴏᴍ ʙᴏʏs’ ɴᴇɪɢʜʙᴏᴜʀ, ᴀɴᴅ ɪᴛs ɴᴏᴡ ʙᴇᴇɴ ᴀ ʏᴇᴀʀ sɪɴᴄᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ᴍᴏᴠᴇᴅ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴏᴜsᴇ ɴᴇxᴛ ᴅᴏᴏʀ.</h5><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: right\">➤</h5><h5 style=\"text-align: right\">⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ☀︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡ ﾟ☁︎｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ｡ ⋆｡ ﾟ⋆｡</h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 143, 152)\">ཐི STORY GALLERY ཋྀ</span></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 481px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/y4a0ns.png\"></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 143, 152)\">ཐི THEIR MAIN CARDS ཋྀ</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a h